#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "mutant power armor"
msgid_plural "mutant power armors"
msgstr[0] "突變動力裝甲"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'mutant power armor'}.
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "The %s engages."
msgstr "%s啟動。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant power armor'}
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid ""
"A modified suit of DoubleTech Power Armor, Mk. II-H.Designed to be used with"
" mutated anatomy in the _REDACTED_ project,it stayed a proof of concept "
"since the _REDACTED_ lifecycle was too short."
msgstr ""
"一套經過改裝的DoubleTech動力裝甲，Mk. II-"
"H型。設計用於_REDACTED_項目中突變解剖結構的使用，由於_REDACTED_的生命週期太短，它僅停留在概念驗證階段。"

#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "mutant power armor (active)"
msgid_plural "mutant power armors (active)"
msgstr[0] "突變動力裝甲（激活狀態）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'mutant power armor (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'mutant power armors (active)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'heavy power armor helmet (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'heavy power armor helmets (active)'}.
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "Turn off"
msgstr "關閉"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'mutant power armor (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'mutant power armors (active)'}.
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "The %s disengages."
msgstr "%s關閉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant power armor (active)', 'str_pl': 'mutant
#. power armors (active)'}
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid ""
"A modified suit of DoubleTech Power Armor, Mk. II-H.Designed to be used with"
" mutated anatomy in the _REDACTED_ project,it stayed a proof of concept "
"since the _REDACTED_ lifecycle was too short.  It is currently turned on, "
"activate it to turn it off."
msgstr ""
"一套經過改裝的DoubleTech動力裝甲，Mk. II-"
"H型。設計用於_REDACTED_項目中突變解剖結構的使用，由於_REDACTED_的生命週期太短，它僅停留在概念驗證階段。它目前處於開啟狀態，激活它以關閉。"

#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "heavy power armor helmet"
msgid_plural "heavy power armor helmets"
msgstr[0] "重型動力裝甲頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy power armor helmet'}
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid ""
"A power armor helmet designed for use with the modified DoubleTech Power "
"Armor, Mk. II-H.Like its accompanying suit, it was never mass produced since"
" the lifespan of _REDACTED_ soldiers was too short, so only the blueprints "
"remained."
msgstr ""
"一款為改裝版DoubleTech動力裝甲Mk. II-"
"H型設計的動力裝甲頭盔。與其配套的裝甲一樣，由於_REDACTED_士兵的壽命太短，它從未大規模生產，因此只留下了藍圖。"

#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "heavy power armor helmet (active)"
msgid_plural "heavy power armor helmets (active)"
msgstr[0] "重型動力裝甲頭盔（激活狀態）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'heavy power armor helmet (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'heavy power armor helmets (active)'}.
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid "The %s powers down."
msgstr "%s 已關閉電源。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy power armor helmet (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'heavy power armor helmets (active)'}
#: .\Mutated_arsenal.json
msgid ""
"A power armor helmet designed for use with the modified DoubleTech Power "
"Armor, Mk. II-H.Like its accompanying suit, it was never mass produced since"
" the lifespan of _REDACTED_ soldiers was too short, so only the blueprints "
"remained ."
msgstr ""
"一款專為改進型雙科技動力裝甲 Mk. II-H 設計的動力裝甲頭盔。與其配套的裝甲一樣，由於 _已編輯_ "
"士兵的壽命過短，該頭盔從未大規模生產，僅留下了藍圖。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Alexs Mutant Power Armor"
msgstr "亞歷克斯的突變動力裝甲"

#. ~ Description for Alexs Mutant Power Armor
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds Power Armor usable by all mutations lines, to make mutations a little "
"less suckier"
msgstr "添加適用於所有突變路線的動力裝甲，讓突變體驗不那麼糟糕"
